title: Close Family
description: ‘Daeman’ had been adopted into a rich family as a little boy but while they called him son, his life was no different than a servant’s. His heart would pound whenever he saw ‘Najeong’, the only family member who was nice to him, even until he grew up to become a robust youth. Now, his beautiful sisters and stepmother who used to abuse him have begun to take notice of Daeman as a man…
